{"tid":1656123,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"《不屈進行曲》繼國歌之後 全世界入黎同我學唱呢首！","createTime":"2019-10-15T12:08:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T00:54:19.000Z","uid":109345,"like":56,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"636bbefe6951a159b8923c151415c7d7abcf4bed","tid":1656123,"uid":109345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:08:44.000Z","msg":"除左願榮光歸香港 下次齊人可以唱埋呢首<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>《不屈進行曲》 《March of the Indomitable》</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ryqGOGig_AI&amp;t=9s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DryqGOGig_AI%26t%3D9s&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLJtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=57fa32ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ryqGOGig_AI&amp;t=9s</a><br />\n《不屈進行曲》<br />\n作曲: thomas dgx yhl<br />\n作詞: thomas dgx yhl, lk, 青棍幫, 眾連登仔<br />\n編曲: thomas dgx yhl , oldcaveman, octad, kotu, bp<br />\nMixing: Stewin, Oldcaveman, 阿歷毛烈岑<br />\nMastering: Oldcaveman, Stewin<br />\n歌詞:   (請唱告眾)<br />\nA1<br />\n來同行        看見嗎<br />\n大地上       不屈的心<br />\n告眾義士   即使險惡 <br />\n也奮力 來驅走 昏暗<br />\nA2 <br />\n在黎明前   你聽見嗎<br />\n是濁霧下   鏗鏘吼聲<br />\n告眾弟妹   不屈的你<br />\n會照亮明天的 香港<br />\nC1 <br />\n為大義  來一起奮抗戰<br />\n讓熱淚  和鮮血 沒白掉<br />\n銘記  眾同伴獻身 約誓 <br />\nC2 <br />\n願萬代  仍堅守這要塞<br />\n讓願望  能歸依這家邦<br />\n在 絕地 屹立 共建光輝<br />\n將正義    歸萬眾<br />\n大義：正道；大道理。代表正義的道理<br />\n家邦: 是指家與國<br />\n歸依: 歸於, 依附<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n超重要"},{"pid":"e4e9fb2aa2578a612fe1ea20dae58c9156aa81e0","tid":1656123,"uid":109345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:09:36.000Z","msg":"push！！！<br />\n大家識唱未？？？"},{"pid":"ef66af860b03cc3e8221f4f468fcdda225f7dcd8","tid":1656123,"uid":109345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:11:23.0